channel.title: [PI]- Duplicated Objects. *SELF-Solved*
channel.description:
Alright I am trying to create an agility course.. But I have 3 rows of almost the same objects.. How do I solve this problem so that when I click on the 2nd row of them it takes me to a different XY Pos, instead of where the first row takes me?
Any help is appreciated. *Please help fast.
EDIT: I just deleted the dupped objects and added: [code]c.absY +2; c.absX +1;[/code]
